INTRODUCTION TO CLOUD COMPUTING

What I learn in this course:

1.Define cloud computing and explain its essential characteristics, history, the business case for cloud, and emerging technologies enabled by cloud

2.Describe the cloud service (IaaS, Saas, Paas) & deployment models (Public, Private, Hybrid), and its infrastructure - VMs, Networking, Storage

3.Explain emerging Cloud related trends including Hybrid Multicloud, Microservices, Serverless, Cloud Native, DevOps and Application Modernization

4.Create a Cloud account and work hands-on with Cloud services, such as Object Storage
